.Sh NAME
.Nm bdpmic
.Nd ROHM BD718x7 Power Management IC
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "bdpmic* at iic?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the voltage regulators in the ROHM BD71837
and BD71847 Power Management ICs.
